extends getting-started

block append pageVariables
    - var moduleTitle = "Package and repo links"

block subContent

    .c-display
        h2 Package and repo links
        p If you want to contribute to development, you can clone the repository for the design system website at:
        pre
            code git clone git@github.com:smartcoop/design.git

        p The Smart Design System uses <a href="https://bedrockapp.org/">Bedrock</a> to generate a static site for the design system. Instructions on how to use Bedrock and run the development stack locally can be found on the <a href="https://github.com/smartcoop/design">front page of the repo</a>.

        p Currently, there is no npm package for the CSS.

        h3 Repo & issue management
        p The repo is at <a href="https://github.com/smartcoop/design">github.com/smartcoop/design</a> . Issues are listed at <a href="https://github.com/smartcoop/design/issues">github.com/smartcoop/design/issues</a> .

        h3 Contributing
        p You can contribute to this project in several ways:
        ul
            li Create a pull request, that improves the code
                ul
                    li Look at open issues for inspiration
                    li Discuss an open issue if you need more information to solve it
            li Create an issue that describes a comment you have, a problem or bug
